import React from 'react'
import {StyleSheet, View, Text, TouchableOpacity} from 'react-native'

const Homebar = () =>{
    return (
        <View style={styles.homebar}>
            <View style={styles.boxContent}>
                <TouchableOpacity>
                    <Text>1</Text>
                </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.boxContent}>
                <TouchableOpacity>
                    <Text>2</Text>
                </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.boxContent}>
                <TouchableOpacity>
                    <Text>3</Text>
                </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.boxContent}>
                <TouchableOpacity>
                    <Text>4</Text>
                </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>
        </View>
    )
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
    homebar:{
        backgroundColor: "blue",
        flex: 4,
        flexDirection: 'row',
        alignItems: 'center'
    },
    boxContent:{
        backgroundColor: 'red',
        flex: 1,
    }
})

export default Homebar
